Description=Cozy is an app-based personal cloud you host at home. It turns a low-cost${Newline}piece of hardware like a Raspberry Pi 2 or an online VPS into a powerful app${Newline}platform. It comes with common applications: a contacts manager, a calendar, a${Newline}webmail and a filebox. An Android app allows you to sync your contacts,${Newline}calendars and files with your mobile. Last but not least, the Cozy Community${Newline}has built many personal tools like a feed reader, a bank operation manager or${Newline}an IRC client (100 000 apps were downloaded in 2015).
